---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="about" description="who, what, why.">
  <div class="page-stage">
    <div class="page-title-block">
      <div class="page-kicker">~/about</div>
      <h1 class="page-title">about</h1>
      <p class="page-subtitle">who, what, why.</p>
    </div>

    <article class="prose">
      <p>
        I'm <strong>canberkefe</strong>. This site is where I keep public research notes,
        lab setups, methodology, and learning progress.
      </p>

      <h2>focus</h2>
      <p>
        Vulnerability research, reverse engineering, firmware analysis. Currently
        digging into FortiGate VM research, boot/init flow analysis, and reproducible
        security research workflows.
      </p>

      <h2>now</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>FortiGate VM internals — boot flow, init scripts, kernel module surface</li>
        <li>Building a reproducible lab for firmware unpacking + emulation</li>
        <li>Working through CTFs (TryHackMe, HackTheBox) and writing them up</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>contact</h2>
      <p>
        Email: <a href="mailto:contact@canberkefe.dev">contact@canberkefe.dev</a><br />
        PGP: <a href="/pgp.txt">/pgp.txt</a> — please encrypt anything sensitive.<br />
        GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/canberkefe">@canberkefe</a>
      </p>

      <blockquote>
        opinions my own. nothing on this site should be construed as advice or
        authorization to test systems you don't own.
      </blockquote>
    </article>
  </div>
</Base>
